#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an9.51"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an9.51:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 9 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 9 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an9.51:0.2"
msgid "5. Sāmaññavagga "
msgstr "5. Similarity "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an9.51:0.3"
msgid "51. Diṭṭhadhammanibbānasutta "
msgstr "51. Extinguishment in the Present Life "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "an9.51:1.1"
msgid "“‘Diṭṭhadhammanibbānaṃ diṭṭhadhammanibbānan’ti, āvuso, vuccati. "
msgstr "“Reverend, they speak of ‘extinguishment in the present life’. "

msgctxt "an9.51:1.2"
msgid "Kittāvatā nu kho, āvuso, diṭṭhadhammanibbānaṃ vuttaṃ bhagavatā”ti? "
msgstr "In what way did the Buddha speak of extinguishment in the present life?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "an9.51:2.1"
msgid "“Idhāvuso, bhikkhu vivicceva kāmehi … pe … paṭhamaṃ jhānaṃ upasampajja viharati. "
msgstr "“First, take a mendicant who, quite secluded from sensual pleasures … enters and remains in the first absorption. "

msgctxt "an9.51:2.2"
msgid "Ettāvatāpi kho, āvuso, diṭṭhadhammanibbānaṃ vuttaṃ bhagavatā pariyāyena … pe …. "
msgstr "To this extent the Buddha spoke of extinguishment in the present life in a qualified sense. … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "an9.51:3.1"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, āvuso, bhikkhu sabbaso nevasaññānāsaññāyatanaṃ samatikkamma saññāvedayitanirodhaṃ upasampajja viharati, paññāya cassa disvā āsavā parikkhīṇā honti. "
msgstr "Furthermore, take a mendicant who, going totally beyond the dimension of neither perception nor non-perception, enters and remains in the cessation of perception and feeling. And, having seen with wisdom, their defilements come to an end. "

msgctxt "an9.51:3.2"
msgid "Ettāvatāpi kho, āvuso, diṭṭhadhammanibbānaṃ vuttaṃ bhagavatā nippariyāyenā”ti. "
msgstr "To this extent the Buddha spoke of extinguishment in the present life in a definitive sense.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an9.51:3.3"
msgid "Dasamaṃ. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an9.51:3.4"
msgid "Sāmaññavaggo pañcamo. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli4.455, sc4
msgctxt "an9.51:4.1"
msgid "Sambādho kāyasakkhī paññā, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an9.51:4.2"
msgid "Ubhatobhāgo sandiṭṭhikā dve; "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an9.51:4.3"
msgid "Nibbānaṃ parinibbānaṃ, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an9.51:4.4"
msgid "Tadaṅgadiṭṭhadhammikena cāti. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p class="endsutta">
msgctxt "an9.51:4.5"
msgid "Paṭhamo paṇṇāsako samatto. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
